 at the Cyrus Poonawalla Group for managing its strategy, investment & finance. He shall continue to be as Non-Executive Director on the Board of Poonawalla Fincorp,"" the exchange filing read. So far this year, shares of HDFC Bank has tumbled over 15 percent, as against 3 percent decline in the Bank Nifty index.
